author: David Fischer
title: YG Offers to Perform “F*ck Donald Trump” at Inauguration for $4 Million USD
text:
Over the last few days the music acts for Donald Trump’s inauguration ceremony have been announced, including the likes of Toby Keith, Jennifer Holiday, and 3 Doors Down. Beyoncé helped ring in President Barack Obama’s second term, this year’s lineup for January 19 is looking a little different. If you are not a fan of the current line-up, you might get lucky, as one of the music world’s most outspoken Trump critics has offered his services for the inauguration over Twitter last night. Compton’s own YG proposed to play his track “Fuck Trump” at the inauguration for $4 million.
I'll perform Fuck Donald Trump at his inauguration for $4,000,000
— YG (@YG) January 15, 2017
